t”.</li>\r\n<li style=\"list-style: none\"><br>\r\n<br></li>\r\n<li>Brad Micklea, Codenvy COO and Che Committer will be giving a lightning talk <strong>May 2nd at 12 pm in the Developer Zone</strong> on how Red Hat is using Factories to radically simplify how developers can experiment with JBoss EAP.</li>\r\n<li style=\"list-style: none\"><br>\r\n<br></li>\r\n<li>We have a pod in the IoT section of the Red Hat booth where we\'ll be presenting Eclipse Che plus Red Hat OpenShift, along with the Eclipse IoT projects all working together as a full stack open source IoT solution.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; Margin: 30px 0 30px\">If you haven\'t had a chance to register for Red Hat Summit yet, get your tickets today!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/e90AuY02000YAm0ig39Pr0b\" class=\"btn\" style=\"Margin-bottom: 25px; background: #000000; border-radius: 4px; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; display: inline-block; line-height: 50px; max-width: 300px; padding-left: 5%; padding-right: 5%; text-decoration: none; color:#00ff8c;\"\r\n>Register for Red Hat Summit</a><br>\r\n<br></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding: 0\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" style=\"border-spacing:0; font-family:sans-serif; color:#333333; background-color:#000000; \" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"space\" style=\"padding: 0;height: 20px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 0px 20px 0px 15px; class=\"><img src=\"http://pages.codenvy.com/rs/519-AYY-549/images/Codenvywordmarkwhite-400.png\" width=\"30%\" alt=\"Codenvy Logo\" style=\"border: 0;height: auto;padding-left:20px;padding-top:10px;\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td style=\"padding:20px 20px; width:100%; text-align:left; \" class=\"mktEditable\" id=\"footer_text\" ><p style=\"color: #ffffff;font-size: 16px;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 10px;\"><a href=\r\n\"http:/