(944,'[Seafile用户论坛]摘要','2016-10-10 13:36:01',0,0,'noreply@bbs.seafile.com','lawren653815@gmail.com','','',NULL,NULL,57,'<table style=\"border: 20px solid #eee;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px 10px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n    <a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; color: #0088cc\">\n      <img src=\"https://bbs.seafile.com/uploads/default/original/1X/f9f1620f4062db2d003fca2d16ce2ae554249e49.png\" style=\"max-height: 35px; min-height: 35px; height: 35px;\" alt=\"Seafile 用户论坛\">\n    </a>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"background-color: #fff; padding: 10px 10px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\n    在你上一次于 九月 7访问后，<a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; color: #0088cc\">Seafile 用户论坛</a>的新内容摘要。\n\n      <hr style=\"background-color: #ddd; height: 1px; border: 1px;\">\n      <h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0 20px 0;\">热门帖子</h3>\n\n\n        <div>\n          <a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com/t/seafile/1019\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699; line-height:1.5em;; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; color: #0088cc\">部署多台seafile服务，每台都要有各自的数据库吗？</a>\n          <br>\n          <a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com/c/server\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699; line-height:1.5em;; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; font-size: 0.857em; white-space: nowrap; display: inline-block; position: relative; line-height: 1; margin-right: 10px;\"><span style=\"background-color: #F7941D;display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px;\"></span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF;color: #222222 !important; vertical-align: text-top; line-height: 1; margin-left: 4px; padding-left: 2px; display: inline;max-width: 150px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" title=\"请将对