(961,'[Seafile用户论坛]摘要','2016-11-14 17:22:24',0,0,'noreply@bbs.seafile.com','lawren653815@gmail.com','','',NULL,NULL,57,'<table style=\"border: 20px solid #eee;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tr>\r\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px 10px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n    <a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; color: #0088cc\">\r\n      <img src=\"https://bbs.seafile.com/uploads/default/original/1X/f9f1620f4062db2d003fca2d16ce2ae554249e49.png\" style=\"max-height: 35px; min-height: 35px; height: 35px;\" alt=\"Seafile 用户论坛\">\r\n    </a>\r\n  </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n  <td style=\"background-color: #fff; padding: 10px 10px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n    在你上次于09月07日访问后，<a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; color: #0088cc\">Seafile 用户论坛</a>的新内容摘要。\r\n\r\n      <hr style=\"background-color: #ddd; height: 1px; border: 1px;\">\r\n      <h3 style=\"margin: 15px 0 20px 0;\">热门帖子</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n        <div>\r\n          <a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com/t/seafile/1521\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699; line-height:1.5em;; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; color: #0088cc\">帮你找回 Seafile 的小绿标</a>\r\n          <br>\r\n          <a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com/c/tutorial\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699; line-height:1.5em;; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; font-size: 0.857em; white-space: nowrap; display: inline-block; position: relative; line-height: 1; margin-right: 10px;\"><span style=\"background-color: #F1592A;display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px;\"></span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF;color: #222222 !important; vertical-align: text-top; line-height: 1; margin-left: 4px; padding-left: 2px; display: inline;max-width: 150px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;\" data-drop-close=\"true\">经验分享</span></a>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n          <div style=\"margin-left: 15px; margin-top: -5px; max-width: 694px;\">\r\n            <p>打开运行,输入 regedit.</p>\r\n<p>移动到<code style=\"background-color: #f1f1ff; padding: 2px 5px;\">HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE-&gt;SOFTWARE-&gt;Microsoft-&gt;Windows-&gt;CurrentVersion-&gt;Explorer-&gt;ShellIconOverlayIdentifiers</code></p>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n        \r\n\r\n        \r\n\r\n        <div>\r\n          <a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com/t/topic/1470\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699; line-height:1.5em;; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; color: #0088cc\">能否增加分享文件列表的排序功能</a>\r\n          <br>\r\n          <a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com/c/suggestions\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699; line-height:1.5em;; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; font-size: 0.857em; white-space: nowrap; display: inline-block; position: relative; line-height: 1; margin-right: 10px;\"><span style=\"background-color: #25AAE2;display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px;\"></span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF;color: #222222 !important; vertical-align: text-top; line-height: 1; margin-left: 4px; padding-left: 2px; display: inline;max-width: 150px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" title=\"请将对 Seafile 的意见或者建议发在这个分类下。\">意见建议</span></a>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n          <div style=\"margin-left: 15px; margin-top: -5px; max-width: 694px;\">\r\n            <p>如题，在登录界面下，文件列表可以按文件名、更新日期等排序的<br>可是在分享出来的链接界面下，却无法实现排序，文件多的话较为麻烦<br>建议增加这个功能<img src=\"http://bbs.seafile.com/images/emoji/emoji_one/wink.png?v=3\" title=\":wink:\" alt=\":wink:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n        \r\n\r\n        \r\n\r\n        <div>\r\n          <a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com/t/seafile/1472\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699; line-height:1.5em;; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; color: #0088cc\">关于seafile文件删除后继续占用空间的问题</a>\r\n          <br>\r\n          <a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com/c/server\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699; line-height:1.5em;; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; font-size: 0.857em; white-space: nowrap; display: inline-block; position: relative; line-height: 1; margin-right: 10px;\"><span style=\"background-color: #F7941D;display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px;\"></span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF;color: #222222 !important; vertical-align: text-top; line-height: 1; margin-left: 4px; padding-left: 2px; display: inline;max-width: 150px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" title=\"请将对 Seafile 服务器端的相关问题发在这个分类下。\">服务器问题</span></a>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n          <div style=\"margin-left: 15px; margin-top: -5px; max-width: 694px;\">\r\n            <p>你好。<br>按照你的方法我尝试了一下，我的操作步骤：<br>1.从资料库中删除一个影片文件；<br>2.重新上传一个小文件；<br>3.删除小文件之后，关闭服务<br>4.执行seaf-gc.sh命令，并重新开启服务</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n        \r\n\r\n        \r\n\r\n        <div>\r\n          <a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com/t/topic/1501\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699; line-height:1.5em;; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; color: #0088cc\">在客户端删除了文件，服务器端没有释放相应的容量</a>\r\n          <br>\r\n          \r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n          <div style=\"margin-left: 15px; margin-top: -5px; max-width: 694px;\">\r\n            <p>我用的是Windows服务器版本，使用了GC工具，还是不会清除已经删除的文件，除非我把整个资料库彻底删除后，使用GC工具才能清除。</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n        \r\n\r\n        \r\n\r\n        <div>\r\n          <a href=\"http://bbs.seafile.com/t/6-0-5/1485\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699; line-height:1.5em;; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #006699;; color: #0088cc\">升级 6.0.5 失败，报数据库问题</a>\r\n          <br>\r\n          <a href=\"http://bbs.seaf