(987,'EclipseChe5Released:Multi-MachineRuntimesandmuchmore','2017-01-13 06:25:12',0,0,'product-team@codenvy.com','lawren653815@gmail.com','','',NULL,NULL,57,'<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\" >\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\r\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><!--[if !mso]><!-->\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\"><!--<![endif]-->\r\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n<title>Eclipse Che 4.7</title>\r\n<!--[if (gte mso 9)|(IE)]>\r\n  <style type=\"text/css\">\r\n    table {border-collapse: collapse;}\r\n  </style>\r\n  <![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\nbody {\r\nmargin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%; background-color: #f7f7f7;\r\n}\r\nimg {\r\npadding: 0;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body style=\"background:#f7f7f7; margin:0; min-width:100%; padding:0; \" bgcolor=\"#F7F7F7\" ><center class=\"wrapper\" style=\"-ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; table-layout:fixed; width:100%; \" ><div class=\"webkit\" style=\"max-width:600px; \" ><!--[if (gte mso 9)|(IE)]>\r\n      <table width=\"600\" align=\"center\">\r\n      <tr>\r\n      <td>\r\n      <![endif]-->\r\n<table class=\"outer\" align=\"center\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; background:#ffffff; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin:0 auto; max-width:600px; width:100%; \" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" ><tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" class=\"bg-dpurple mktEditable\" id=\"header\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; background:#333333; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \" bgcolor=\"#525C86\" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 30px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://pages.codenvy.com/rs/519-AYY-549/images/logo-eclipseche.png\" alt=\"Eclipse Che\" class=\"logo\" style=\"height: auto; padding: 0; width: 180px\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" class=\"bg-dpurple mktEditable\" id=\"hero\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; background:#525c86; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \" bgcolor=\"#525C86\" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 0 0px; text-align: left; width: 600px\" align=\"left\"><!-- <img src=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: auto; padding: 0; width: 100%; display: block;\"> --></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" class=\"mktEditable\" id=\"intro\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 0px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\">\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 34px; line-height: 38px; font-weight: normal; margin: 40px 0 5px;padding-bottom:10px;\">Eclipse Che 5 Released</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Eclipse Che is the open source foundation of Codenvy - Che releases give Codenvy users a sneak-peek into what will be coming soon to their enterprise installs.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThis is a major release for Che and includes over 1300 commits from 60 contributors. Codenvy will be releasing it\'s own 5.0 with all the Che features and many more, in the coming weeks.</p>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/O0s0rgiY02009AP50P0b2AY\"\r\n><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*BI6hYQqxatY9_gxJDd7D0g.gif\" style=\"img-align:center; width:500px;padding-bottom:10px;\" alt=\"Che 5.0\" width=\"500\"></a><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/O0s0rgiY02009AP50P0b2AY\" class=\"btn\" style=\"Margin-bottom: 25px; background: #FDB940; border-radius: 4px; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; display: inline-block; line-height: 45px; max-width: 300px; padding-left: 10%; padding-right: 10%; text-decoration: none\"\r\n>Read the Release Notes</a>\r\n<hr style=\"border-color: #d1d3d4; border-style: solid; border-width: 10px 0 0\">\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 30px; line-height: 38px; font-weight: normal; margin: 30px 0px 5px;\"></h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 30px 0 5px;\">Docker Compose Runtimes:</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Develop against a production runtime using multi-container Docker Compose files in your workspace. You can run as many containers networked together in your workspace as you want to properly reflect the target run environment.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 40px 0 5px;\">Workspace Agents</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Dynamically inject developer services to convert production runtimes into developer workspaces. Services include language intellisense, SSH access, debuggers and more.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 40px 0 5px;\">Enhanced PHP Support</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">The new PHP stack comes with full intellisense, a built-in debugger, certified runtimes and a dedicated project type.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 40px 0 5px;\">Language Server Protocol</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Che now supports the open language server protocol which provides syntax highlighting, code analysis, error checking and auto-completion. Today, there is support for JSON, C#, Java, PHP and TypeScript language servers and support for nearly 20 more language servers in the future.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; text-transform:uppercase; margin: 40px 0 5px;\">Other Great Features:</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">You can read more about all the features of Eclipse Che 5 in the release note blog.</p>\r\n<ul style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">\r\n<li>New (fun!) CLI</li>\r\n<li>CLI Assemblies</li>\r\n<li>Workspace Snapshots</li>\r\n<li>Docker Exec Agent</li>\r\n<li>Stack Editor</li>\r\n<li>New Debuggers</li>\r\n<li>SSH</li>\r\n<li>Desktop Sync</li>\r\n<li>Split & Resize</li>\r\n<li>Docker Store Certification</li>\r\n<li>Chedir</li>\r\n<li>RedHat OpenShift</li>\r\n<li>Contributor-Friendly Docs</li>\r\n<li>More Responsive</li>\r\n<li>Bitnami Stacks</li>\r\n<li>CentOS</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/O0s0rgiY02009AP50P0b2AY\" class=\"btn\" style=\"Margin-bottom: 25px; background: #FDB940; border-radius: 4px; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; display: inline-block; line-height: 45px; max-width: 300px; padding-left: 10%; padding-right: 10%; text-decoration: none\"\r\n>Read the Release Notes</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding: 0\">\r\n<table width=\"100%\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-spacing: 0; color: #666666; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\">\r\n<hr s