loper workspaces. Start with Docker or Compose, “dev mode” the workspace with agents for debugging, terminals, SSH, sync, and intellisense, and then connect any IDE, whether your favorite desktop IDE or our built-in Eclipse Che Web IDE.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCodenvy has also been Dockerized, which means you can install Codenvy in minutes on any operating system with Docker including Mac and Windows!</p>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/K00igAY00Pv32QbAr0290Y0\"\r\n><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*4HXw07w7yeHVyxUk-0ELlQ.gif\" style=\"img-align:center; width:500px;padding-bottom:10px;\" alt=\"Codenvy 5.0\" width=\"500\"></a><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/K00igAY00Pv32QbAr0290Y0\" class=\"btn\" style=\"Margin-bottom: 25px; background: #FDB940; border-radius: 4px; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; display: inline-block; line-height: 45px; max-width: 300px; padding-left: 10%; padding-right: 10%; text-decoration: none\"\r\n>Read the Release Notes</a>\r\n<hr style=\"border-color: #d1d3d4; border-style: solid; border-width: 10px 0 0\">\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 30px; line-height: 38px; font-weight: normal; margin: 30px 0px 5px;\"></h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 30px 0 5px;\">Dockerized Codenvy:</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Install a private Codenvy anywhere Docker runs.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 40px 0 5px;\">Fair Source 3 (Free) User License</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Built-in, non-expiring, 3 user license.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 40px 0 5px;\">New CLI</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Offline installation, simple configuration, and data backup.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 40px 0 5px;\">Consolidate Databases</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Because a single database is easier to manage.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 40px 0 5px;\">Auditing Capabilities</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Track workspace usage and license compliance.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 40px 0 5px;\">Built-in Documentation</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Access Codenvy docs from your own server</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 40px 0 5px;\">LDAP Integration</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Synchronization and authentication for LDAP / AD.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; text-transform:none; margin: 40px 0 5px;\">Che 5 Improvements:</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">You can read more about all the features of Eclipse Che 5 in the release note blog.</p>\r\n<ul style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">\r\n<li>Docker Compose Runtimes</li>\r\n<li>Workspace Snapshots</li>\r\n<li>Workspace Snapshots</li>\r\n<li>Docker Exec Agent</li>\r\n<li>Stack Editor</li>\r\n<li>Language Server Protocol</li>\r\n<li>New Debuggers</li>\r\n<li>SSH</li>\r\n<li>Desktop Sync</li>\r\n<li>Split & Resize</li>\r\n<li>Desktop Sync</li>\r\n<li>Docker Store Certification</li>\r\n<li>PHP</li>\r\n<li>Chedir</li>\r\n<li>More Responsive</li>\r\n<li>Contributor-Friendly Docs</li>\r\n<li>More Responsive</li>\r\n<li>Bitnami Stacks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/K00igAY00Pv32QbAr0290Y0\" class=\"btn\" style=\"Margin-bottom: 25px; background: #FDB940; border-radius: 4px; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; display: inline-block; line-height: 45px; max-width: 300px; padding-left: 10%; padding-right: 10%; text-decoration: none\"\r\n>Read the Release Notes</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding: 0\">\r\n<table width=\"100%\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-spacing: 0; color: #666666; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding: 0\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" style=\"border-spacing:0; font-family:sans-serif; color:#333333; background-color:#292E4B; \" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"space\" style=\"padding: 0;height: 20px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 0px 20px 0px 15px; class=\"><img src=\"http://pages.codenvy.com/rs/519-AYY-549/images/logo%403x.png\" width=\"30%\" alt=\"Codenvy Logo\" style=\"border: 0;height: auto;padding-left:6px;padding-top:10px;\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td style=\"padding:20px 20px; width:100%; text-align:left; \" class=\"mktEditable\" id=\"footer_text\" ><p style=\"color: #ffffff;font-size: 16px;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 10px;\"><a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/n0Ar04R02i9P0YY0A200bvg\" style=\"color: #ffffff;border-bot