ges.codenvy.com/rs/519-AYY-549/images/logo-eclipseche.png\" alt=\"Eclipse Che\" class=\"logo\" style=\"height: auto; padding: 0; width: 180px\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" class=\"bg-dpurple mktEditable\" id=\"hero\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; background:#525c86; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \" bgcolor=\"#525C86\" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 0 0px; text-align: left; width: 600px\" align=\"left\"><!-- <img src=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: auto; padding: 0; width: 100%; display: block;\"> --></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" class=\"mktEditable\" id=\"intro\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 0px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\">\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 34px; line-height: 38px; font-weight: normal; margin: 40px 0 5px;padding-bottom:10px;\">Release Notes: Eclipse Che 5.2</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Eclipse Che is the open source foundation of Codenvy - Che releases give Codenvy users a sneak-peek into what will be coming soon to their enterprise installs.<br>\r\n<br></p>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/F2AYP00po0A0r2Hi000Yb9g\"\r\n><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/0*edXEAjPTBCXeCo0E.\" style=\"img-align:center; width:560px;padding-bottom:10px;\" alt=\"Che 5.2\" width=\"560\"></a><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/F2AYP00po0A0r2Hi000Yb9g\" class=\"btn\" style=\"Margin-bottom: 25px; background: #FDB940; border-radius: 4px; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; display: inline-block; line-height: 45px; max-width: 300px; padding-left: 10%; padding-right: 10%; text-decoration: none\"\r\n>Read the Release Notes</a>\r\n<hr style=\"border-color: #d1d3d4; border-style: solid; border-width: 10px 0 0\">\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; padding-top:20px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Docker Compose Support in Chefiles:</strong> Multi-machine workspaces automatically generated from your repo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Multi-Che Support:</strong> Easily run multiple Che instances on the same host.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>File-Context Git Actions:</strong> File context menu for common git actions.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>PHP Composer:</strong> Support for the popular PHP scaffolding utility.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Updated PHP Tutorial:</strong> Try all the new PHP intellisense and debugging.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Memory & Disk Checks on Startup:</strong> Resource checks when starting Che.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Networking Checks on Startup:</strong> Checks browser to workspace and server to workspace connectivity to avoid common network issues.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Improved CLI Output:</strong> More detail has been added to the info command plus you can generate a diagnostic snapshot for problems.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 26px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 40px 0 5px;\"></h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>CPU Limiting for Docker Builds:</strong> Docker builds can be CPU intensive so they now carry CPU limits to prevent starving other workspaces.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Restart a Failed Workspace:</strong> You can now easily restart workspaces that didn’t start correctly the first time.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Python Intellisense:</strong> Syntax highlighting and hover-over help docs.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: normal; font-family:\'open sans\',helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; text-transform:none; margin: 40px 0 5px;\"><br>\r\nOther Great Features:</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 10px\">You can read more about all the features of Eclipse Che 5.2 in the release note blog.</p>\r\n<ul style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 30px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">\r\n<li>Automatic updates of workspace config</li>\r\n<li>Simplified Dashboard build</li>\r\n<li>Proper cache control header for resources</li>\r\n<li>Added Vert.x stack</li>\r\n<li>Improved find and navigate to file capabilities in IDE</li>\r\n<li>Allowed to get verbose mode on unison utility when using CLI sync command</li>\r\n<li>Add possibility to catch websocket url error</li>\r\n<li>Updated the styles for popups</li>\r\n<li>Add support of docker compose file in Chefile</li>\r\n<li>Input-boxes with ‘required’ attribute are marked with asterisk</li>\r\n<li>Add pretty formatting in bats tests CLI image and add bats-assert helper functions</li>\r\n<li>Added documentation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/Q0HY0AY0Aq2Pi092b00pgr0\" class=\"btn\" style=\"Margin-bottom: 25px; background: #FDB940; border-radius: 4px; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; display: inline-block; line-height: 45px; max-width: 300px; padding-left: 10%; padding-right: 10%; text-decoration: none\"\r\n>Read the Release Notes</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding: 0\">\r\n<table width=\"100%\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-spacing: 0; color: #666666; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\">\r\n<hr style=\"border-color: #d1d3d4; border-style: solid; border-width: 10px 0 0\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" class=\"mktEditable\" id=\"tier2\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\">\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 34px; line-height: 38px; font-weight: normal; Margin: 10px 0 20px;\">Eclipse Che</h1>\r\n<p style=\"color: #666666;font-size: 18px;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 10px;\"><a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/F2AYP00rq0A0r2Hi000Yb9g\" style=\"line-height: 30px;color: #525c86;border-bottom: 1px solid #525c86;text-decoration: none;\"\r\n>Release Notes</a><br>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/P00090bAPY0rsg0H0ArY2i2\" style=\"line-height: 30px;color: #525c86;border-bottom: 1px solid #525c86;text-decoration: none;\"\r\n>Changelog</a><br>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/Lig2YY0020tH0AsAr0P0b09\" style=\"line-height: 30px;color: #525c86;border-bottom: 1px solid #525c86;text-decoration: none;\"\r\n>Get Eclipse Che</a><br>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/p0g00A02tY0i0u9YbP0rAH2\" style=\"line-height: 30px;color: #525c86;border-bottom: 1px solid #525c86;text-decoration: none;\"\r\n>Docs</a><br>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/q2YA0b0APu09gH02Y0rv00i\" style=\"line-height: 30px;color: #525c86;border-bottom: 1px solid #525c86;text-decoration: none;\"\r\n>Source Code</a><br></p>\r\n