r new look         What we\'ve been up to:      Podcast: How L.S.P. Could Help IDEs The New Stack Makers podcast recently hosted our very own Tyler Jewell &amp; Brad Micklea. In the episode, they discussed the latest release of Codenvy’s cloud-based IDE, and how it could greatly benefit team-based development along with the launch of LSP. Listen to it here.           Introducing Codenvy Teams Codenvy is now the only cloud workspace with packages for Individuals, Teams, and Enterprises. Learn about the new Codenvy Teams here             Release Notes: Codenvy 5.6 Intelligent Commands + Improvements to Teams           Devoxx US &amp; Eclipse Converge Roundup Over half a dozen members of the Codenvy &amp; Eclipse Che team descended upon San Jose, California for the very first Devoxx US and Eclipse Converge conference. Read the recap             Follow us on Twitter and LinkedIn Stay up to date with everything Codenvy at @CodenvyHQ on Twitter and @Codenvy on LinkedIn.           White Paper: Localhost is Killing Software Delivery The era of DevOps is upon us. Learn why companies are moving away from localhost environments and choosing on-demand developer workspaces. Get the white paper               &nbsp;     Overview // Products // Documentation // Blog   Codenvy, Inc 33 New Montgomery Suite 1500, San Francisco, CA 94105             This email was sent to lawren653815@gmail.com. If you no longer wish to receive these emails you may unsubscribe at any time.',1),
