: 20px; display: inline-block; line-height: 45px; max-width: 300px; padding-left: 10%; padding-right: 10%; text-decoration: none\"\r\n>Read the Release Notes</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding: 0\">\r\n<table width=\"100%\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-spacing: 0; color: #666666; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\">\r\n<hr style=\"border-color: #d1d3d4; border-style: solid; border-width: 10px 0 0\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" class=\"mktEditable\" id=\"tier2\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\">\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 34px; line-height: 38px; font-weight: normal; Margin: 10px 0 20px;\">Eclipse Che</h1>\r\n<p style=\"color: #666666;font-size: 18px;margin: 0;margin-bottom: 10px;\"><a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/v0gA09hO0bPYAro3Y02i000\" style=\"line-height: 30px;color: #525c86;border-bottom: 1px solid #525c86;text-decoration: none;\"\r\n>Changelog</a><br>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/wYAY9gbAP0000r3p00i2P0h\" style=\"line-height: 30px;color: #525c86;border-bottom: 1px solid #525c86;text-decoration: none;\"\r\n>Get Eclipse Che</a><br>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/VAYq000bh30Y200APgirQ90\" style=\"line-height: 30px;color: #525c86;border-bottom: 1px solid #525c86;text-decoration: none;\"\r\n>Docs</a><br>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/F3AYP00Rr0A0r2hi000Yb9g\" style=\"line-height: 30px;color: #525c86;border-bottom: 1px solid #525c86;text-dec