lt=\"Eclipse Che\" class=\"logo\" style=\"height: auto; padding: 0; width: 180px\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" class=\"bg-dpurple mktEditable\" id=\"hero\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; background:#525c86; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \" bgcolor=\"#525C86\" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 0 0px; text-align: left; width: 600px\" align=\"left\"><!-- <img src=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: auto; padding: 0; width: 100%; display: block;\"> --></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" class=\"mktEditable\" id=\"intro\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 0px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\">\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 34px; line-height: 38px; font-weight: normal; margin: 40px 0 5px;padding-bottom:10px;\">Join the Che Community!</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; Margin: 1px 0 20px\">In the last year, Eclipse Che underwent a year of exponential growth, from initial introduction to being the most active project in the Eclipse Foundation. This is no small feat and that’s thanks to our community.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe contributors and maintainers of Che have dedicated countless nights and weekends to making improvements and pushing fixes that we ship bi-weekly. Without the help of the community, we know we could never have gotten to where we are now - almost 4,000 GitHub stars and tens of thousands of daily users, thank you.</p>\r\n<img src=\"http://pages.codenvy.com/rs/519-AYY-549/images/Screen Shot 2017-04-20 at 10.33.35 AM.png\" style=\"img-align:center; width:500px;padding-bottom:20px;\" alt=\"Che Community\" width=\"500\">\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">If you love Che but aren’t sure how to start contributing, here are some quick and easy ways to get started:</p>\r\n<ol style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #525c86;font-weight:bold;\">Star and watch the repo:</span> <a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/Ak0I0gAY209b3ri00P050AY\" style=\"color:#000000;\"\r\n>It helps others find Che and keeps you in-the-loop on changes.</a></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #525c86;font-weight:bold;\">Help with docs:</span> Even if you’re shy to start with code changes, <a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/o026900Jk003rA0gAYYbiP0\" style=\"color:#000000;\"\r\n>we always need help with docs</a>. <a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/Lig2YY00307k0AKAr0P0b09\" style=\"color:#000000;\"\r\n>Fix a known issue</a>, file a new issue or start a PR for a change you think we need.</li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #525c86;font-weight:bold;\">File a bug:</span> Have a pet peeve with Che - <a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/g80Ag9P0i203YY0bA000Lkr\" style=\"color:#000000;\"\r\n>file an issue</a> so that it can be addressed.</li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #525c86;font-weight:bold;\">Fix a bug:</span> The only thing we like better than community-filed <a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/u99000AYgP0b0M02kriAY30\" style=\"color:#000000;\"\r\n>bugs</a> are <a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/db0Pr3a9ki0YA00YgN020A0\" style=\"color:#000000;\"\r\n>community-fixed bugs</a>!</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">Thank you again for being part of the Che community and we hope you’ll take a moment to contribute.</p>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/Ak0I0gAY209b3ri00P050AY\" class=\"btn\" style=\"Margin-bottom: 25px; background: #FDB940; border-radius: 4px; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; disp