(1054,'Che5.9:UpgradedLanguageServerSupport,JavaTestingSupport,andmore!','2017-04-28 23:51:13',0,0,'product-team@codenvy.com','lawren653815@gmail.com','','',NULL,NULL,57,'<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\" >\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\r\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><!--[if !mso]><!-->\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\"><!--<![endif]-->\r\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n<title>Eclipse Che 4.7</title>\r\n<!--[if (gte mso 9)|(IE)]>\r\n  <style type=\"text/css\">\r\n    table {border-collapse: collapse;}\r\n  </style>\r\n  <![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\nbody {\r\nmargin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%; background-color: #f7f7f7;\r\n}\r\nimg {\r\npadding: 0;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body style=\"background:#f7f7f7; margin:0; min-width:100%; padding:0; \" bgcolor=\"#F7F7F7\" ><center class=\"wrapper\" style=\"-ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; table-layout:fixed; width:100%; \" ><div class=\"webkit\" style=\"max-width:600px; \" ><!--[if (gte mso 9)|(IE)]>\r\n      <table width=\"600\" align=\"center\">\r\n      <tr>\r\n      <td>\r\n      <![endif]-->\r\n<table class=\"outer\" align=\"center\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; background:#ffffff; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin:0 auto; max-width:600px; width:100%; \" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" ><tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" class=\"bg-dpurple mktEditable\" id=\"header\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; background:#333333; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \" bgcolor=\"#525C86\" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://pages.codenvy.com/rs/519-AYY-549/images/logo-eclipseche.png\" alt=\"Eclipse Che\" class=\"logo\" style=\"height: auto; padding: 0; width: 180px\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" class=\"bg-dpurple mktEditable\" id=\"hero\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; background:#525c86; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \" bgcolor=\"#525C86\" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 0 0px; text-align: left; width: 600px\" align=\"left\"><!-- <img src=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: auto; padding: 0; width: 100%; display: block;\"> --></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr ><td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding:0; \" ><table width=\"100%\" class=\"mktEditable\" id=\"intro\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; border-spacing:0; color:#666666; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; \" ><tr>\r\n<td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 0px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\">\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 30px; line-height: 38px; font-weight: normal; margin: 40px 0 5px;padding-bottom:10px;\">Upgraded Language Server Support, Java Testing Support, and more!</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">The 5.9 release of Che is now available, the update comes with a number of new features and improved overall performance for users. Users will now have access to the latest Language Server support and improved Java Testing support, faster database queries, archetype command for CLI, WildFly Swarm stack, and improvements to the editor.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Eclipse Che is the open source project of Codenvy - Che releases give Codenvy users a sneak-peek into what will be coming soon to their enterprise installs.</em><br></p>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/q3YA0b0APe09gp02Y0rw00i\"\r\n><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*odRhoHYraw2o82mYQYVH2A.png\" style=\"img-align:center; width:560px;padding-bottom:10px;\" alt=\"Che 5.9\" width=\"560\"></a><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<a href=\r\n\"http://mkto-ab050050.com/q3YA0b0APe09gp02Y0rw00i\" class=\"btn\" style=\"Margin-bottom: 25px; background: #FDB940; border-radius: 4px; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; display: inline-block; line-height: 45px; max-width: 300px; padding-left: 10%; padding-right: 10%; text-decoration: none\"\r\n>Read the Release Notes</a>\r\n<hr style=\"border-color: #d1d3d4; border-style: solid; border-width: 10px 0 0\">\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 24px; line-height: 28px; font-weight: normal; margin: 30px 0 5px;padding-bottom:10px;\">5.9 Features:</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; padding-top:0px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Language Server Support:</strong> Che language server now supports Eclipse LSP4J.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Java Testing Support:</strong> Filter successful tests from result view, better navigation and, lots of usability tweaks.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Performance:</strong> Faster database queries.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Archetype Command for CLI:</strong> Simpler approach to generate, build and run custom Che.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>WildFly Swarm Stack:</strong> Build WildFly Swarm based applications using the default WildFly Swarm stack.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\"><strong>Editor Improvement:</strong> Preview images in separate browser tab.</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 24px; line-height: 28px; font-weight: normal; margin: 30px 0 5px;padding-bottom:10px;\">Other Notable Enhancements:</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; Mar