(1063,'CheTakesCenterStageatRedHatSummit','2017-05-07 11:38:35',0,0,'product-team@codenvy.com','lawren653815@gmail.com','','',NULL,NULL,57,'<head >\r\n\r\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n  <!--[if !mso]><!-->\r\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\r\n  <!--<![endif]-->\r\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n  <title>Eclipse Che 4.7</title>\r\n  \r\n  <!--[if (gte mso 9)|(IE)]>\r\n  <style type=\"text/css\">\r\n    table {border-collapse: collapse;}\r\n  </style>\r\n  <![endif]-->\r\n  \r\n</head><body bgcolor=\"#f7f7f7\" style=\"background: #f7f7f7; margin: 0; min-width: 100%; padding: 0\" ><img alt=\" \" height=\"1\" src=\"http://r20.rs6.net/on.jsp?a=1127869207900&r=3&c=20085bb0-31c0-11e7-9395-d4ae5275b3f6&d=1127880537799&ch=20d23b60-31c0-11e7-9451-d4ae5275b3f6&ca=505a9b2a-7e3a-41a1-839d-4cb4792d4c5d&o=https://imgssl.constantcontact.com/ui/images1/s.gif\" width=\"1\"/>\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\nbody {\r\nmargin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%; background-color: #f7f7f7;\r\n}\r\nimg {\r\npadding: 0;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n  <center class=\"wrapper\" style=\"-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; table-layout: fixed; width: 100%\">\r\n    <div class=\"webkit\" style=\"max-width: 600px\">\r\n      <!--[if (gte mso 9)|(IE)]>\r\n      <table width=\"600\" align=\"center\">\r\n      <tr>\r\n      <td>\r\n      <![endif]-->\r\n      <table class=\"outer\" align=\"center\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background: #ffffff; border-spacing: 0; color: #666666; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 600px; width: 100%\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">\r\n        <tr>\r\n          <td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding: 0\">\r\n            <table width=\"100%\" class=\"bg-dpurple mktEditable\" id=\"header\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background: #333333; border-spacing: 0; color: #666666; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\" bgcolor=\"#525c86\">\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\">\r\n                  <img src=\"http://pages.codenvy.com/rs/519-AYY-549/images/logo-eclipseche.png\" alt=\"Eclipse Che\" class=\"logo\" style=\"height: auto; padding: 0; width: 180px\">\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n            </table>\r\n          </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n          <td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding: 0\">\r\n            <table width=\"100%\" class=\"bg-dpurple mktEditable\" id=\"hero\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background: #525c86; border-spacing: 0; color: #666666; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\" bgcolor=\"#525c86\">\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 0  0px; text-align: left; width: 600px\" align=\"left\">\r\n                 <!-- <img src=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: auto; padding: 0; width: 100%; display: block;\"> -->\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n            </table>\r\n          </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n          <td class=\"one-column\" style=\"padding: 0\">\r\n            <table width=\"100%\" class=\"mktEditable\" id=\"intro\" style=\"-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-spacing: 0; color: #666666; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\">\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td class=\"inner contents\" style=\"padding: 0px 20px; text-align: left; width: 100%\" align=\"left\">\r\n                  <h1 style=\"color: #525c86; font-size: 34px; line-height: 38px; font-weight: normal; margin: 40px 0 5px;padding-bottom:10px;\">Eclipse Che + Openshift.io in the Red Hat Summit Keynote</h1>\r\n                 <p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; Margin: 1px 0 20px\">  \r\nRed Hat Summit was an exciting time for the Eclipse Che project  we were center stage during the Summit Keynote where Paul Cormier announced the launch of openshift.io and Eclipse Che was demonstrated to the 6000 Summit attendees. <a alt=\"http://openshift.io/\" href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001i4Jq28V-bYVUnjmwBhyuQ1bMJoTE8rN7HnY_OoCKvPBXpWN7BJY_6Yuwhm3G4Yrfjgp93dOW73WtuNInVnfi93cRBFpFW8HRwZb-lNm6aVerB4p0wwikbY3uSJlhiD-TcTfVB162XO1_Iuum6sFc8c4yBRGf05nyXQw0u751iOU=&c=7PU4DCMtcXleP4kiL3hF78bSq6WR1W1847gKpLozJHnPodVvf3A3gQ==&ch=8ZWnYaBm09EeJb32bfAU294MyTI6B6tFMTC_JCpn0pB3b0mAT0BK5Q==\">OpenShift.io</a> is an exciting product - a developer-focused cloud offering based Eclipse Che, OpenShift, fabric8, Insights and a new issue tracker developed by Red Hat.\r\n<br /><br />\r\n <a alt=\"https://che.eclipse.org/openshift-io-and-eclipse-che-97a89e045f28\" class=\"btn\" href=\"http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001i4Jq28V-bYVUnjmwBhyuQ1bMJoTE8rN7HnY_OoCKvPBXpWN7BJY_6Yuwhm3G4YrfIG9zPunmDeW1_Tne0wIh3FIMhSvRXVdRIusXZ8WGvveg7AaTS_ILXrrelly5gqegJjyMInRT8aJrI9xoex5-vXMJt6m3gd_XXBsg4N4a3ACZfb8YZK9t2V4cjbvlnINN-ziL7qvVmoqN-FDNafpinLC_6W4CRQk4&c=7PU4DCMtcXleP4kiL3hF78bSq6WR1W1847gKpLozJHnPodVvf3A3gQ==&ch=8ZWnYaBm09EeJb32bfAU294MyTI6B6tFMTC_JCpn0pB3b0mAT0BK5Q==\" style=\"Margin-bottom: 25px; background: #FDB940; border-radius: 4px; color: #fff; font-size: 20px; display: inline-block; line-height: 45px; max-width: 300px; padding-left: 10%; padding-right: 10%; text-decoration: none\">Learn about OpenShift and Che</a>\r\n<br /><br />\r\nRed Hat has ported Che to run inside OpenShifts Kubernetes-based pods, making it easy for a developer to code, build, debug and deploy in OpenShift. Openshift.io will utilize these Che workspaces to create a seamless cloud development experience and enable teams across the globe to collaborate more efficiently.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; Margin: 1px 0 30px\">  \r\nIts not just OpenShift that is giving Eclips